subject: Track and Field
Interscholastic Athletics
lead_paragraph: Six years ago, in the New Balance Games, Alan Webb ran 3 minutes 59.86 seconds in the invitation mile. Now a world-class runner, Webb ran the same race Saturday and won by 10 yards in 3:56.7.
